{{vgname|F1 2002}}是[[美商藝電|美商藝電]]於2002年發行的[[競速遊戲|競速遊戲]]，對應[[Xbox_(遊戲機)|Xbox]]、[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]、[[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]和[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]。遊戲改編自[[2002年世界一级方程式锦标赛|2002年世界一级方程式锦标赛]]。

== 評價 ==

《F1 2002》獲[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]網站2002年6月「月度電腦遊戲」之亞軍<ref name="gotm">{{cite web | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20021204003624/http://gamespot.com/gamespot/features/pc/gotm/070502/index.html | url=http://gamespot.com:80/gamespot/features/pc/gotm/070502/index.html | title=PC Game of the Month, June 2002 | author=The Editors of ''GameSpot PC'' | date=July 5, 2002 | work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archivedate=2002-12-04 | url-status=dead | accessdate=2021-02-05 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。遊戲還獲得該網站年度年度「最佳電腦競速遊戲」和「最佳GameCube競速遊戲」亞軍<ref name="bestworst2002">{{cite web | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030207155400/http://gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/bestof2002/ | url=http://gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/bestof2002/ | title=''GameSpot''{{'}}s Best and Worst of 2002 | author=''GameSpot'' Staff | date=December 30, 2002 | work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archivedate=2003-02-07 | url-status=dead | accessdate=2021-01-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

